ce:section.ce:para:
In daily life, Sn4+ and AA are present in the environment or medicine which are intimately associated with people’s lives. Therefore, we evaluated the ability of the probes to detect Sn4+ and AA in real samples. After adding different concentration of Sn4+ to actual samples, the achieved recoveries remained within a satisfactory range of 89.35 % – 115.05 % (Table 1
                        ), which are similar with the results of standard method (Fig. S4 and Table S2), indicating CDs have high accuracy to detect Sn4+.We conducted analysis of AA content in both standard vitamin C tablets and effervescent vitamin C tablets. The recovery was 91.11 % and 94.19 %, respectively (Table 2
                        ). The findings indicate that CDs retain their capability to precisely evaluate Sn4+ and AA in intricate environments.
